'''Sobo''' is a spirit or [[loa]] in the [[Haitian Vodou]] religion. He is the spirit of thunder and is always depicted and served with his inseparable companion/brother [[Bade (loa)|Bade]], who is the spirit of wind. Together they are represented by the [[Roman Catholic Church|Catholic]] image of [[Saints Cosmas and Damian]]. He is probably [[West Africa]]n in origin and a flaming ram is his symbol.

